keywords.name: Anim
keywords.description: When this minion dies, return it to the field with 1 health.

keywords.name: Bane
keywords.description: When damage is dealt by this, destroy the non-player target.

keywords.name: Bastion
keywords.description: Absorb one hit of damage from the target before disappearing.

keywords.name: Bind
keywords.description: Prevent the target from performing actions until the start of their next turn.

keywords.name: Call
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when the Card is played from the hand.

keywords.name: Chain
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when this card is played after another.

keywords.name: Copy
keywords.description: Generates a copy of a target.

keywords.name: Cusp
keywords.description: An effect that occurs at the end of the turn.

keywords.name: Charge(x)
keywords.description: A card that can be played X many times from hand for the same cost.

keywords.name: Evoke
keywords.description: Summon a minion from your deck.

keywords.name: Find
keywords.description: Finds an existing card from a selection. Added to the hand by default.

keywords.name: Form
keywords.description: Generates a new card from a selection. Added to the hand by default.

keywords.name: Fury
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when the target is damaged.

keywords.name: Gag
keywords.description: Removes any/all effects from the target.

keywords.name: Giant(x)
keywords.description: A minion that summons powerful token cards in x other spaces (varies depending on the fiend).

keywords.name: Hail
keywords.description: Find 3 cards from your deck, pick one to put on top.

keywords.name: Invoke
keywords.description: Activates the hero power of another card.

keywords.name: Lift(x)
keywords.description: An effect is active when certain mana threshold is reached.

keywords.name: Link
keywords.description: A State shared between adjacent cards.

keywords.name: Mime
keywords.description: Can be played as many times as possible, for the base mana cost.

keywords.name: Nexus
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when this card enters the Nexus space at the center of the board, or after a Rook Swap.

keywords.name: Overkill
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when damage is greater than the health of the target.

keywords.name: Pact
keywords.description: An effect that becomes after after (x) friendly minions die while this is in hand.

keywords.name: Raid(x)
keywords.description: Able to attack (x) times per turn.

keywords.name: Rale
keywords.description: An effect that applies when a Minion or Hero has been destroyed after being played to the board.

keywords.name: Ressurrect
keywords.description: Brings back a Minion that has been destroyed on the board.

keywords.name: Rite
keywords.description: Complete a set of specific steps to obtain a reward.

keywords.name: Rook
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when a Rook enters a Rook space on the sides of a board.

keywords.name: Root
keywords.description: An effect that occurs at the start of the game.

keywords.name: Sap
keywords.description: Damage dealth restores Health to the Player.

keywords.name: Sly
keywords.description: Cannot be targeted by Spells or Scale Powers.

keywords.name: Spell Damage
keywords.description: Increases the damage done by Spells, including Traps.

keywords.name: Stand
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when this survives damage.

keywords.name: Storm
keywords.description: Can attack any enemy character immediately.

keywords.name: Trade
keywords.description: Shuffle this card back into your deck and draw a new card.

keywords.name: Veil
keywords.description: Cannot be targeted until this attacks.

keywords.name: Ward
keywords.description: Enemies must attack this, or other Ward Fiends.

keywords.name: Weight
keywords.description: An effect that occurs when you activate a Scale Power.
